 Isidore Augustine,

40
00:05:52,938 --> 00:05:54,871
AKA Nicholas August?

41
00:05:54,871 --> 00:05:56,356
- Yeah.

42
00:05:56,356 --> 00:05:58,150
- And you waived the right
 to have an attorney present.

43
00:05:58,150 --> 00:05:59,013
Is that correct?

44
00:05:59,980 --> 00:06:01,153
- My attorney is present.

45
00:06:04,364 --> 00:06:05,295
- Let's get to it.

46
00:06:06,435 --> 00:06:09,817
I'm Special Agent
 Winslow of the FBI,

47
00:06:10,991 --> 00:06:12,855
Organized Crime Division.

48
00:06:15,271 --> 00:06:17,100
I'm confused about one
 thing, your residence.

49
00:06:17,100 --> 00:06:20,897
