240
00:16:09,969 --> 00:16:11,971
[men grunting]

241
00:16:11,971 --> 00:16:16,976
[legs thudding]
[Nick groaning]

242
00:16:30,299 --> 00:16:31,749
- Nicholas.

243
00:16:32,957 --> 00:16:35,753
Is this the ganef you
 say was following us?

244
00:16:35,753 --> 00:16:38,928
Oh God, get, get.

245
00:16:38,928 --> 00:16:40,482
Nicholas, come, come,
 come, shh, shh, shh.

246
00:16:40,482 --> 00:16:41,655
Come, sit down.

247
00:16:42,829 --> 00:16:44,244
Why are you here?

248
00:16:45,418 --> 00:16:47,213
- That's what I'd
 like to know, Manny.

249
00:16:47,213 --> 00:16:48,145
You tell me.

250
00:16:49,284 --> 00:16:50,423
And what's an East
 Coast attorney

251
00:16:50,423 --> 00:16:52,735
doing with the syndicate
in Palm Springs?

252
00:16:52,735 --> 00:16:54,841
- Oh, they're clients.

253
00:16:54,841 --> 00:16:58,534
You lie down with dogs,
you get up with fleas.

254
00:16:58,534 --> 00:16:59,501
I count you with your--

255
00:16:59,501 --> 00:17:00,329
- No, no.

256
00:17:01,330 --> 00:17:03,022
This is not legal.

257
00:17:03,022 --> 00:17:04,540
- Legal?

258
00:17:04,540 --> 00:17:06,266
What's the difference?

259
00:17:06,266 --> 00:17:07,681
We're lawyers.

260
00:17:07,681 --> 00:17:10,788
We deal in the business
of interpretations.

261
00:17:15,206 --> 00:17:17,553
That's not why you're
 here, is it, my son?

262
00:17:21,419 --> 00:17:22,248
- No.

263
00:17:24,457 --> 00:17:28,288
- [sighs] I have always dreaded
that this day would come.

264
00:17:30,635 --> 00:17:33,224
And now you shall
 have that you seek.

